## Class Naming Convention (Client-First)
```
[component]_[element]-[modifier]
```

### Examples:
- `navbar_component` - Main navbar wrapper
- `navbar_link` - Navigation link
- `navbar_link-current` - Current page state
- `hero_heading` - Hero section heading
- `hero_heading-large` - Large variant
- `button_primary` - Primary button
- `button_secondary` - Secondary button
- `section_header` - Section header wrapper
- `margin-top_medium` - Utility class
```

