### Interactions & Animations
```markdown
# Webflow Interactions Library

## Page Load Animations
### Staggered Fade In
- Trigger: Page load
- Elements: Hero content children
- Animation:
  1. Set initial: opacity 0, transform Y 20px
  2. Animate: opacity 1, transform Y 0
  3. Stagger: 100ms delay between elements

## Scroll Animations
### Reveal on Scroll
- Trigger: Element enters viewport
- Offset: 20% from bottom
- Animation:
  1. Initial: opacity 0, transform Y 40px
  2. Final: opacity 1, transform Y 0
  3. Duration: 600ms, ease out

### Parallax Background
- Trigger: While scrolling in view
- Element: Background image
- Animation: Transform Y based on scroll position

## Hover Interactions
### Card Lift
- Trigger: Mouse hover
- Animation:
  1. Transform Y: -8px
  2. Box shadow: increase
  3. Duration: 300ms

### Button Scale
- Trigger: Mouse hover
- Animation:
  1. Transform scale: 1.05
  2. Duration: 200ms

## Menu Animations
### Mobile Menu Open
- Trigger: Click menu button
- Animation sequence:
  1. Menu: height 0 → auto, opacity
  2. Menu items: staggered fade in
  3. Icon: transform to X

### Dropdown Menu
- Trigger: Hover on nav item
- Animation:
  1. Dropdown: opacity, transform Y
  2. Arrow: rotate 180deg
```

### Custom Code Snippets
```html
<!-- Webflow Custom Code Examples -->

<!-- HEAD CODE: Fonts & Analytics -->
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>

<!-- Global site tag (gtag.js) - Google Analytics -->
<script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=GA_MEASUREMENT_ID"></script>
<script>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());
  gtag('config', 'GA_MEASUREMENT_ID');
</script>

<!-- BODY CODE: Current Year -->
<script>
document.querySelectorAll('[data-year]').forEach(el => {
  el.textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
});
</script>

<!-- Form Submission to External Service -->
<script>
const form = document.querySelector('[data-form="contact"]');
form.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
  e.preventDefault();
  const formData = new FormData(form);

  try {
    await fetch('https://api.example.com/contact', {
      method: 'POST',
      body: formData
    });
    // Show success state
    form.style.display = 'none';
    document.querySelector('[data-success]').style.display = 'block';
  } catch (error) {
    document.querySelector('[data-error]').style.display = 'block';
  }
});
</script>

<!-- Smooth Scroll for Anchor Links -->
<script>
document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
  anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({
      behavior: 'smooth'
    });
  });
});
</script>
```

